    "Their work has shown promise of using free text explanations for interpreting the biased or prejudiced implications of the content leading to more thoughtful content moderation.",
    "We show that this category has discovered at least 9 more categories of safety, albeit these categories are sparse.",
    "This category also allows for easy extensibility to future safety risk categories.",
